name: token-saver
description: RTK token optimization proxy. Transparent CLI proxy that reduces
  LLM token consumption by 60-90% via PreToolUse hook auto-rewrite. Use this
  skill when checking token savings, troubleshooting hook issues, manually
  optimizing commands, or when the user mentions rtk, token cost, token usage,
  output compression, or command filtering.
version: 1.0.0
emoji: 🛠️
